OL,6,FTriple killer Valdo Calocane is to be
OL,7,Fsentenced today for the manslaughter
OL,8,Fof students Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,9,FO'Malley-Kumar and school caretaker
OL,10,FIan Coates in a spate of attacks in
OL,11,FNottingham.
OL,13,FCalocane, formerly of Forest Fields,
OL,14,FNottingham pleaded not guilty to
OL,15,Fmurder and
OL,17,FHe is due to be sentenced on Thursday
OL,18,Fat the city's crown court.
