OL,6,FCalocane also admitted three counts of
OL,7,Fattempted murder relating to
OL,8,Fpedestrians he deliberately targeted
OL,9,Fwith a van he had stolen from Mr
OL,10,FCoates in the early hours of 13 June
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FJudge Mr Justice Turner, who will
OL,14,Fsentence Calocane, will decide between
OL,15,Fimposing a "hybrid" life sentence with
OL,16,Fa hospital direction or a hospital
OL,17,Forder under the Mental Health Act.
