OL,6,FThe defence lawyer added:
OL,7,F"Schizophrenia is a well-established,
OL,8,Flong-established mental disease that
OL,9,Fcan strike anyone and will strike 1%
OL,10,Fof the population through no fault of
OL,11,Ftheir own.
OL,13,F"The clearest evidence in this case is
OL,14,Favailable... it (the mental illness)
OL,15,Fstarted in late 2019 and he was
OL,16,Fdiagnosed as a paranoid schizophrenic
OL,17,Fin May 2020.
OL,19,F"No fabrication, no exaggeration, no
OL,20,Fconcoction ` this unwanted visitor to
OL,21,Fhis life hit him. That's the fact."
