OL,6,FMr Webber and Miss O'Malley-Kumar,
OL,7,Fboth 19, were walking home from an end-
OL,8,Fof-term night out when they were
OL,9,Fstabbed repeatedly by Calocane in
OL,10,FIlkeston Road, Radford.
OL,12,FMiss O'Malley-Kumar tried to protect
OL,13,Fher friend and
OL,15,FMr Webber's mother broke down in tears
OL,16,Fas the court heard Calocane used a
OL,17,Fdagger to stab him multiple times with
OL,18,F"devastating violence".
