OL,6,FCalocane then went on to kill 65-year-
OL,7,Fold school caretaker Mr Coates around
OL,8,Fan hour later on Magdala Road,
OL,9,FMapperley, before stealing his van and
OL,10,Fhitting three pedestrians.
OL,12,FTwo of Mr Coates' sons said his death
OL,13,Fhad "rocked everyone's world," adding:
OL,14,F"Nobody deserves this but he
OL,15,Fdefinitely didn't."
OL,17,FMr Justice Turner said he will pass
OL,18,FCalocane's sentence at 11.30am on
OL,19,FThursday.
